75
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,560
The money went missing during morning assembly.

76
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,290
At that time,

77
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:14,980
Qi Shuo,

78
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,920
Gu Ming, Qiu Qian,

79
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,850
