85
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,240
But I had no idea

86
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,280
when the money was put there.

87
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,280
I suspect

88
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:33,610
