122
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:16,000
Why are you calling me again?

123
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:18,920
Don't hang up,

124
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:20,400
I need to ask you something.

125
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:22,530
Do you remember that milk fee incident

126
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,440
in our class back then?

127
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,440
Yeah, I remember.

128
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,940
I have some recollection.

129
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:27,600
What's up?

130
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,520
I just

131
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,160
