132
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,840
do you remember who

133
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,320
took it back then?

134
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,940
Did they ever find out?

135
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,240
Coming!

136
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,260
Qi Shuo,

137
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:39,880
