147
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,250
Could it have

148
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,440
just rubbed off on it?

149
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,760
Before we complete our investigation,

150
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,220
don't jump to conclusions

151
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,920
