155
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:29,500
I've caused trouble for everyone

156
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,440
and got Zhenzhen involved in this mess.

157
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,700
Don't blame yourself.

158
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,440
This matter

159
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,520
still requires all of us to investigate thoroughly

160
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,850
so we can clear her name.

161
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,130
Let's go.

162
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:46,140
On behalf of Zhenzhen,

163
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,600
thank you.

164
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:00,770
Going to eat?

165
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,520
You guys go ahead,

166
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:03,650
I'll join you later.

167
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,440
I'm leaving now.

168
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:04,760
Bye.

169
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,440
Let's go.

170
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,760
Darling Qianqian,

171
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,220
